data.description:
3 br 2 ba 2000+ sq ft Custom Craftsman style. Well maintained home a short walk from the beach on approx 1/2 acre park like lot. Located on a cul-de-sac in the desirable Seabird Beach loop neighborhood. 

Home features laminate floors, 9 ft ceilings, oversize custom windows. large kitchen with newer Kitchen Aid stainless package, stainless topped island, gas downdraft range, quartz counters with tile backsplash. Cozy 5 piece master bath with Jacuzzi jetted tub, 30 gal WH with instant hot water, his and hers walk in closets, and direct access to private deck with covered dual lounge 30 jet spa. Bedrooms 2 &3 are oversize. Large garage with utility sink, work bench, and kennel. Beautifully landscaped yard fenced for kids and pets!

Also fiber cement siding (Hardie) and new roof in 2014.

Owner is former realtor. Pre qualified and appointment for showing. Email for more info. Bring your buyers agent if you so desire.

Also, the adjacent almost 1/2 acre buildable tax lot is available.
data.whatILove: We love the open feel, sunset views, and the short walk the beautiful Bandon Beach. Sitting on the cozy front porch.
